'''Tudayt''' d [[ajjed]] amezwaru ideg ttamnen medden belli yella yiwen [[yakuc]] (Rebbi) kan. Isem-is s [[tɛebrit]] : Yahvé. Udayen ur nezmir ara ad neṭqen isem-agi axaṭer ɣur-sen ḥram. Yakuc g tudayt yesɛa lemluk i t-ttɛawanen, yuzen rrusel ɣur medden akken ad ttamnen yis-es. Yahvé yextar agdud : agdud n [[israyil]] akken ad necren awal-is.

Udayen ttganin lmasiḥ, iwumi a ten-yeslek u ad yexleq tamurt n Israyil tamqqrant: Erezt Israyil, lmasiḥ-agi ɣur-s tazmert n wessidir wid yemmuten. Udayen ur ttamnen ara belli [[Ɛisa]] d lmasiḥ axaṭer ur yezmir ad yexdem ayen yettwura deg wedlis-nsen ([[turat]]), ur yexliq ara tamurt n israyil tameqqrant, ur ten-yeslik ara seg ifassen rruman, tella daɣen yiwet tamacahutt ɣef Ɛisa sɣur imasiḥiyen, mi yasen-d-yenna bell netta d lmasiḥ, udayen ṭṭfen-t u ddan yid-es ɣer tameqqbert, nnan-as : "ssidir wid yemmuten!". Udayen n tura ur qbilen ara Ɛisa d lmasiḥ axaṭer deg [[tamasiḥt|tmasiḥt]], Ɛisa d mmi-s n Rebbi, ɣur Udayen, Rebbi ur yesɛi mmi-s.

Mazal ar tura udayen ttganin lmasiḥ. Yuɣ lḥal, udayen xelqen tamurt n Israyil mebla tallalt n lmasiḥ g 1948, kra n wudayen nnan-d bell ayagi d leḥram, yessefk ad gganin lmasiḥ.
 

